{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And also some of them who were in the Russian Army, were running things there, because-- and, and also the local [? roussiens, ?] who were the other side of the city-- the periphery of the city, they lived.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They also were in charge of the running the city because the Czechs were there at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But then soon after, the Czechs got kicked out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because Stalin decided to, to annex that part to Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he, at that time, already started to get rid of the Czech soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Although they were still there, but he was putting in slowly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That was the time-- the period that I was there, is when the Czech soldiers were being replaced.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The Czech police, the Czech Army, the Czech city hall representative were being replaced with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there and didn't get a very good reception, even from the local Jewish people, because they were telling me they're communist.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And did I have any property?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It belongs to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I should give it to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't want to go into it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The guy who really was after me the mostly is a multimillionaire in this city now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't seem to be that much of a communist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a communist only for the day against me, but not against himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wanted to stay in my hometown till the war would wind up to see if anybody or any members came back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I said, is-- I got involved with this man who joined the militia, he called it-- also got a gun.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he knew that my father had gold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wanted to get it as badly as he can.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
